Company Summary
Robert Half International Inc. is the world's largest specialized provider of temporary and permanent personnel in the fields of accounting and finance. Its divisions include ACCOUNTEMPS-Registered Trademark- and ROBERT HALF-Registered Trademark-, providers of temporary and permanent personnel, respectively, in the fields of accounting and finance.   





 







