ROBERT HALF INTERNATIONAL INC. Competition

   Robert Half International carries the full load of personnel services. The company places temporary and permanent staff through eight divisions: Accountemps, Robert Half Finance and Accounting, Robert Half Legal, OfficeTeam (general administrative), Robert Half Technology (information technology), Robert Half Management Resources (senior level professionals), and The Creative Group (advertising, marketing, and Web design). The firm also publishes job reports and surveys on the latest employment trends and annual salary guides to track pay trends, and has an internal audit and risk consulting division in Protiviti.
  






